text: Wolfgang Girardi (19 April 1928 - 28 March 2018) was an Austrian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
